column2: SELECT   c.ID_T, c.ID, c.RA as RA_#, c.DEC as DEC_#, n.objID, n.distance, p.objID, p.specObjID, p.ra as ra_#, p.dec as dec_#, p.z, p.petroR5#_r, p.petroR5#Err_r, p.petroR9#_r, p.petroR9#Err_r, p.modelMag_u, p.modelMag_g, p.modelMag_r,   p.modelMag_i, p.modelMag_z, p.modelMagErr_u, p.modelMagErr_g, p.modelMagErr_r, p.modelMagErr_i, p.modelMagErr_z, p.extinction_u, p.extinction_g, p.extinction_r, p.extinction_i,  p.extinction_z  FROM   MYDB.TODOS as c       OUTER APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq( c.RA, c.DEC, #) AS n   LEFT JOIN PhotoObjAll AS p ON n.objid=p.objid          INTO mydb.TODOS_salida   ORDER BY c.ID_T
